look for $
if encountred and is active then :
	if it is followed by ?
		expand it to the last exit status
	if it is followed by '
		handle it as a cstring expansion
	if it is followed by \
		handle it a backslash expansion (non standard)
	if it is followed by "
		handle it a double quote exapnsion (non standard)
	else
		expand normaly that is get the name following it and get it value
